">https://www.thehindu.com/entertainment/dance/malavika-sarukkai-plays-arjuna-and-krishna-in-her-forthcoming-production/article29776888.ece</ref> ᱩᱱᱤᱫᱚ ᱟᱹᱰᱤ ᱱᱟᱯᱟᱭ ᱮᱱᱮᱡ ᱰᱷᱟᱝ ᱤᱫᱤ ᱛᱮ ᱩᱱᱤᱭᱟᱜ ᱤᱠᱥᱤᱴᱢᱮᱸᱴ (excitement) ᱫᱚ ᱩᱱᱤ ᱟᱹᱰᱤ ᱱᱟᱯᱟᱭ ᱮᱱᱮᱡ ᱪᱮᱫᱚᱜ ᱞᱟᱹᱜᱤᱫ ᱛᱮ ᱤᱱᱥᱯᱭᱟᱨ (Inspire) ᱠᱮᱫᱟ ᱵᱷᱟᱨᱚᱛᱱᱟᱴᱭᱚᱢ ᱪᱮᱫᱚᱜ ᱮᱦᱚᱵᱽ ᱠᱮᱫᱼᱟ ᱩᱱᱤ ᱾ [[ᱥᱤᱧᱚᱛ ᱥᱚᱨᱠᱟᱨ]] ᱤᱫᱤ ᱛᱮ ᱨᱟᱦᱟ ᱟᱲᱟᱝ ᱜᱟᱭᱟᱱ ᱮᱠᱮᱰᱮᱢᱤ ᱥᱤᱨᱯᱷᱟᱹ ᱮᱢᱟᱫ ᱫᱮᱭᱟ ᱠᱚ,
<ref name="Sangeet Natak AKademi Award">{{cite web|url=http://sangeetnatak.gov.in/sna/awardeeslist.htm |title=Sangeet Natak AKademi Award |publisher=Sangeet Natak AKademi |date=2015 |accessdate=8 February 2015 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150530204253/http://sangeetnatak.gov.in/sna/awardeeslist.htm |archivedate=30 May 2015 }}</ref> ᱟᱨ ᱥᱤᱧᱚᱛ ᱥᱚᱨᱠᱟᱨ ᱤᱫᱤ ᱛᱮ ᱒᱐᱐᱓ ᱨᱮ ᱯᱩᱱᱭᱟ ᱩᱥᱩᱞ ᱥᱤᱧᱚᱛᱤᱭᱟᱹ ᱥᱟᱦᱨᱤ ᱯᱟᱫᱢᱟ ᱥᱨᱤ ᱠᱷᱚᱱ ᱦᱚᱸ ᱢᱟᱱ ᱪᱟᱞ ᱟᱫᱮᱭᱟ ᱠᱚ ᱛᱟᱦᱮᱸᱫ ᱾  <ref name="Padma Awards">{{cite web|url=http://mha.nic.in/sites/upload_files/mha/files/LST-PDAWD-2013.pdf |title=Padma Awards |publisher=Padma Awards |date=2015 |accessdate=6 February 2015 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6U68ulwpb?url=http://mha.nic.in/sites/upload_files/mha/files/LST-PDAWD-2013.pdf |archivedate=15 November 2014 }}</ref>
